          <img src="https://placehold.co/40x40" alt="User Profile" class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full">
          <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-md max-w-2xl">
            <p>Can you help me draft a comprehensive marketing strategy for our new product launch?</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex space-x-3 justify-end">
          <div class="bg-blue-500 text-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-md max-w-2xl">
            <p>I'd be happy to help you develop a marketing strategy. Let's break this down into several key
              components...</p>
          </div>
          <img src="https://placehold.co/40x40" alt="AI Assistant Profile" class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border-t p-4">
        <div class="relative">
          <label for="message-input" class="sr-only">Message input</label>
          <textarea
            id="message-input"
            class="w-full pr-16 pl-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 resize-none"
            rows="3" placeholder="Type your message..."></textarea>
          <div class="absolute inset-y-0 right-0 flex items-center pr-4 space-x-2">
            <button type="button" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-600">
